    "description": "<p>Yamaha Music (Asia) Private Limited is a subsidiary of Yamaha Corporation since 1966. We are a multi-business giant providing many exciting music courses and dealing with various musical related products.<br>\n<br>\nAt Yamaha Music (Asia) Private Limited, we strive, not only for higher music literacy across the nation, but also to promote a love for all kinds of music across all ages. We offer a wide variety of music courses and music related products. That’s the reason why we are the premier music company in Singapore.<br>\n<br>\nYamaha Music (Asia) Private Limited has retail stores, music schools, and a vast network of dealers across Singapore. Fronted by dedicated sales &amp; marketing team and supported by experienced technical and teaching personnel. Yamaha Music (Asia) Private Limited continues to provide quality products and well-researched music education programs for music lovers.<br>\n<br>\nIf you are inspire to become part of Yamaha family, you may look out for the available job opportunities via the following link:<br>\nhttps://sg.yamaha.com/en/about_yamaha/recruitment/index.html <br>\nhttps://sg.yamaha.com/en/education/teaching_career/index.html</p>",
